        <hl1>Bartoli Replaced at Met</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Cecilia Bartoli cancels appearance at Metropolitan Opera's gala Pension Fund Concert because of illness; Olga Borodina will replace her (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Cecilia Bartoli has canceled her appearance at the Metropolitan Opera's gala Pension Fund Concert tomorrow at 5 p.m. because of illness. She is to be replaced by Olga Borodina, who will join Bryn Terfel as a soloist with the Metropolitan Orchestra and Chorus conducted by James Levine.</p>
      </block>
